<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BrainBoost GPSTR Premium Guide</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg1: #f8fbff;
      --bg2: #f6fffb;
      --text: #18212f;
      --muted: #5b6472;
      --white: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      --stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.08);
      --shadow-soft: 0 10px 28px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.05);
      --radius-xl: 30px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
      --blue: #4f8cff;
      --violet: #8b5cf6;
      --pink: #ec4899;
      --green: #22c55e;
      --orange: #fb923c;
      --teal: #14b8a6;
      --kn-default: #6b21a8; /* deep violet for readability */
      --kn-blue: #1d4ed8;
      --kn-green: #047857;
      --kn-orange: #b45309;
      --kn-pink: #be185d;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(139,92,246,0.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(79,140,255,0.14), transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(34,197,94,0.12), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg1), var(--bg2));
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4f8cff 48%, #1cc8a0 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(79, 140, 255, 0.22);
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      isolation: isolate;
    }

    .hero::before,
    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(6px);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .hero::before {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      right: -50px;
      top: -70px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .hero::after {
      width: 170px;
      height: 170px;
      left: -35px;
      bottom: -55px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.35rem;
      line-height: 1.12;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 760px;
      font-size: 1.03rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
    }

    .kannada-text {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #fef9c3;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .badge {
      padding: 9px 13px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .status-grid,
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .status-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .glass-card,
    .card,
    .status-box,
    .highlight {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .status-box {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 20px;
      min-height: 190px;
    }

    .status-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .live-badge {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fff1f2);
      color: #dc2626;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      animation: pulseBadge 1.8s infinite;
    }

    .live-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #ef4444;
    }

    .status-box::before,
    .card::before,
    .highlight::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.28), transparent 45%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .status-app {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,245,245,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #fecaca;
    }

    .status-exam {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(241,246,255,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #bfdbfe;
    }

    .status-hall {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(240,255,248,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #a7f3d0;
    }

    .status-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .status-app .status-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe4e6, #fff7ed); }
    .status-exam .status-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #ede9fe); }
    .status-hall .status-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcfce7, #ccfbf1); }

    .status-box h3 {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .status-box p,
    .card p,
    .card li,
    .highlight {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .kn {
      color: var(--kn-default);
      font-weight: 700;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    .updating {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      color: #2563eb;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .updating::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -120%;
      width: 70%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.9), transparent);
      animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
    }

    .dot-wrap {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #60a5fa;
      animation: blink 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    .dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 80%, 100% { opacity: 0.25; transform: scale(0.84); }
      40% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.08); }
    }

    @keyframes shimmer {
      0% { left: -120%; }
      100% { left: 130%; }
    }

    @keyframes pulseBadge {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(239,68,68,0.18); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(239,68,68,0.28); }
    }

    @keyframes floatButton {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    }
      40% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.08); }
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      margin: 28px 0 12px;
      line-height: 1.18;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .section-title .kn-title {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #0f766e;
      margin-top: 5px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .highlight {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
      margin: 22px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,249,219,0.96), rgba(255,241,242,0.96));
      border-left: 6px solid #f59e0b;
    }

    .card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
      min-height: 100%;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card .kn-title {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #7c3aed;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .card ul { padding-left: 18px; }
    .card li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

    .accent-purple {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(250,245,255,0.96), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #d8b4fe;
    }
    .accent-purple .kn { color: var(--kn-default); }
    .accent-green {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(240,253,244,0.96), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #86efac;
    }
    .accent-green .kn { color: var(--kn-green); }
    .accent-orange {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,247,237,0.96), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #fdba74;
    }
    .accent-orange .kn { color: var(--kn-orange); }
    .accent-pink {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(253,242,248,0.96), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #f9a8d4;
    }
    .accent-pink .kn { color: var(--kn-pink); }
    .accent-blue {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(239,246,255,0.96), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-top: 6px solid #93c5fd;
    }
    .accent-blue .kn { color: var(--kn-blue); }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding: 22px 16px 90px;
      color: #667085;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .sticky-cta {
      position: sticky;
      bottom: 14px;
      z-index: 20;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .sticky-cta button {
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      min-width: 260px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #4f8cff, #14b8a6);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(79,140,255,0.28);
      animation: floatButton 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .sticky-cta button span {
      opacity: 0.92;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-left: 6px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body { padding: 14px; }
      .hero { padding: 24px 18px; border-radius: 26px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.95rem; }
      .hero p { font-size: 0.98rem; }
      .section-title { font-size: 1.4rem; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); }
      .status-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .card, .status-box, .highlight { padding: 18px; border-radius: 20px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      body { padding: 12px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.62rem; }
      .hero p, .card p, .card li, .status-box p, .highlight { font-size: 0.93rem; }
      .badge { font-size: 0.77rem; padding: 8px 11px; }
      .section-title { font-size: 1.24rem; }
      .section-title .kn-title,
      .card .kn-title { font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .card h2, .status-box h3 { font-size: 1.03rem; }
      .grid, .status-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sticky-cta button {
        width: 100%;
        min-width: 0;
        font-size: 0.94rem;
        padding: 14px 18px;
      }
      .live-badge {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        padding: 6px 9px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">✨ Premium BrainBoost Design</div>
      <h1>BrainBoost GPSTR Success Guide</h1>
      <p>
        Crack GPSTR with a smart plan, brief syllabus focus, and consistent practice. BrainBoost helps aspiring teachers learn with clarity, confidence, and daily direction.
        <span class="kannada-text">ಬ್ರೇನ್‌ಬೂಸ್ಟ್ ಜೊತೆ GPSTR ತಯಾರಿ ಇನ್ನಷ್ಟು ಸುಲಭ, ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟ ಮತ್ತು ಯಶಸ್ವಿಯಾಗಲಿ.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">GPSTR Preparation</span>
        <span class="badge">Brief Syllabus</span>
        <span class="badge">Daily Strategy</span>
        <span class="badge">BrainBoost Learning</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="status-grid">
      <div class="status-box status-app">
        <div class="status-top">
          <div class="status-icon">📌</div>
          <div class="live-badge"><span class="live-dot"></span> NEW UPDATE</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Application Date <span class="kn">ಅರ್ಜಿ ದಿನಾಂಕ</span></h3>
        <p>Notification not released yet. Date is updating.</p>
        <span class="kn">ಇನ್ನೂ ಅಧಿಸೂಚನೆ ಬಿಡುಗಡೆಯಾಗಿಲ್ಲ. ದಿನಾಂಕ ನವೀಕರಿಸಲಾಗುತ್ತಿದೆ.</span>
        <div class="updating">Updating <span class="dot-wrap"><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="status-box status-exam">
        <div class="status-top">
          <div class="status-icon">🗓️</div>
          <div class="live-badge"><span class="live-dot"></span> NEW UPDATE</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Exam Date <span class="kn">ಪರೀಕ್ಷಾ ದಿನಾಂಕ</span></h3>
        <p>Exam schedule not announced yet. Updating status shown here.</p>
        <span class="kn">ಪರೀಕ್ಷೆಯ ವೇಳಾಪಟ್ಟಿ ಇನ್ನೂ ಪ್ರಕಟವಾಗಿಲ್ಲ. ಇಲ್ಲಿ ನವೀಕರಣ ತೋರಿಸಲಾಗುತ್ತದೆ.</span>
        <div class="updating">Updating <span class="dot-wrap"><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="status-box status-hall">
        <div class="status-top">
          <div class="status-icon">🎫</div>
          <div class="live-badge"><span class="live-dot"></span> NEW UPDATE</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Hall Ticket <span class="kn">ಹಾಲ್ ಟಿಕೆಟ್</span></h3>
        <p>Hall ticket date not available yet. Please check updates.</p>
        <span class="kn">ಹಾಲ್ ಟಿಕೆಟ್ ದಿನಾಂಕ ಇನ್ನೂ ಲಭ್ಯವಿಲ್ಲ. ನವೀಕರಣಗಳನ್ನು ಪರಿಶೀಲಿಸಿ.</span>
        <div class="updating">Updating <span class="dot-wrap"><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight">
      <strong>Why BrainBoost for GPSTR?</strong><br />
      BrainBoost is not just a study platform. It is a focused learning project designed to make preparation simple, structured, motivating, and exam-oriented for future teachers.<br />
      <span class="kn">GPSTR ಅಭ್ಯಾಸವನ್ನು ಸರಳ, ವ್ಯವಸ್ಥಿತ ಮತ್ತು ಗುರಿ ಆಧಾರಿತವಾಗಿಸಲು ಬ್ರೇನ್‌ಬೂಸ್ಟ್ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ.</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">What is GPSTR?<span class="kn-title">GPSTR ಎಂದರೇನು?</span></h2>
    <div class="card accent-blue">
      <p><strong>GPSTR</strong> is a teacher recruitment exam for graduate primary school teacher posts.</p>
      <p><span class="kn">GPSTR ಎಂಬುದು ಪದವೀಧರ ಪ್ರಾಥಮಿಕ ಶಾಲಾ ಶಿಕ್ಷಕರ ನೇಮಕಾತಿ ಪರೀಕ್ಷೆಯಾಗಿದೆ.</span></p>
      <p>To crack it well, candidates need subject knowledge, pedagogy understanding, language skills, and regular practice.</p>
      <p><span class="kn">ಈ ಪರೀಕ್ಷೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಯಶಸ್ಸು ಪಡೆಯಲು ವಿಷಯ ಜ್ಞಾನ, ಪೆಡಗೋಗಿ ತಿಳುವಳಿಕೆ, ಭಾಷಾ ಕೌಶಲ್ಯ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಯಮಿತ ಅಭ್ಯಾಸ ಅಗತ್ಯ.</span></p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">How BrainBoost Connects to GPSTR Preparation<span class="kn-title">GPSTR ತಯಾರಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಬ್ರೇನ್‌ಬೂಸ್ಟ್ ಹೇಗೆ ಸಹಾಯಕ?</span></h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card accent-purple">
        <h2>1. Clear Learning Path <span class="kn-title">ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟ ಅಧ್ಯಯನ ದಾರಿ</span></h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Breaks big syllabus into simple daily targets<br><span class="kn">ದೊಡ್ಡ ಸಿಲೆಬಸ್ ಅನ್ನು ದಿನನಿತ್ಯದ ಸಣ್ಣ ಗುರಿಗಳಾಗಿ ವಿಭಜಿಸುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Helps students avoid confusion and random study<br><span class="kn">ಅವ್ಯವಸ್ಥಿತ ಓದನ್ನು ತಪ್ಪಿಸಲು ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Keeps preparation focused and step by step<br><span class="kn">ತಯಾರಿಯನ್ನು ಹಂತ ಹಂತವಾಗಿ ಸಾಗಿಸುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card accent-green">
        <h2>2. Smart Revision Support <span class="kn-title">ಚುರುಕಾದ ಮರುಅಭ್ಯಾಸ</span></h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Encourages quick revision through brief points<br><span class="kn">ಸಂಕ್ಷಿಪ್ತ ಅಂಶಗಳ ಮೂಲಕ ಬೇಗ ಮರುಅಭ್ಯಾಸ ಮಾಡಲು ನೆರವಾಗುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Supports memory retention with repeated review<br><span class="kn">ಪುನರಾವರ್ತನೆಯಿಂದ ನೆನಪು ಹೆಚ್ಚುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Useful for weekly and exam-time revision<br><span class="kn">ವಾರದ ಮತ್ತು ಪರೀಕ್ಷಾ ಸಮಯದ ಮರುಅಭ್ಯಾಸಕ್ಕೆ ಉತ್ತಮ</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card accent-orange">
        <h2>3. Motivation and Consistency <span class="kn-title">ಪ್ರೇರಣೆ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಯಮಿತತೆ</span></h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Helps aspirants stay regular every day<br><span class="kn">ಪ್ರತಿ ದಿನವೂ ನಿಯಮಿತವಾಗಿ ಓದಲು ಪ್ರೇರೇಪಿಸುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Builds confidence through planned learning<br><span class="kn">ಯೋಜಿತ ಓದಿನಿಂದ ಆತ್ಮವಿಶ್ವಾಸ ಹೆಚ್ಚುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
          <li>Turns preparation into a disciplined routine<br><span class="kn">ತಯಾರಿಯನ್ನು ಶಿಸ್ತಿನ ಅಭ್ಯಾಸವನ್ನಾಗಿ ಮಾಡುತ್ತದೆ</span></li>
        </ul>
